title: Looking for a tea/few players to play with. I am currently S3. Main support but can also play Top/JG
body:
Hello,
Check me out of Oce.op.gg
http://oce.op.gg/summoner/userName=Kynadr

I am looking for a team or few players to play with on a regular basis. I am Silver 3 currently trying to grind to Gold 5.
I play (ordered from best to worst)
(Support) Nami (currently ranked 303 best Nami player in OCE), Taric 
(Top) Pantheon, Kayle, Heimedinger
(Jungle) Zac, Rammus, Trundle

I play from 7:30/8pm -  10pm most nights (NZ time) 
Main voice chat I use is Curse.
